<br>
We followed another biotech called BCY almost 18mths ago below $0.20. The stock was dead for the longest time and then out of the blue it ran to 0.85 in early November - only to have it collapse 3wks later to 0.20 on negative news !!  Typical biotech investing - requires a stomach of iron.<br>
<br>
The following is from CHR's most recent Sedar filing in case you missed it.<br>
<br>
MESSAGE FROM THE PRESIDENT<br>
<br>
